&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;All Your Skills training sessions are fun and interactive using different methods of learning from team working to self-reflection. You&amp;rsquo;ll also get to work with other volunteers to share your learning. The sessions have been developed to equip you with everything you need in order to be the best in your volunteering role and are led by trained members of staff.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Aim of the session:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;This session will give students the opportunity to refine and share campaign aims and to explore effective campaigning.&nbsp;You will be introduced to a range of tools to plan an effective campaign and will have the opportunity to develop&nbsp;your skills as a campaigner.&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Learning objectives:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&amp;bull;&nbsp;Explore definitions of campaigning&lt;br /&gt;&amp;bull;&nbsp;Identify a clear campaign aim and the principles of effective campaigning&lt;br /&gt;&amp;bull;&nbsp;Create a campaign plan: create a &amp;lsquo;so-that&amp;rsquo; chain for a campaign (part of the Theory of Change planning model)&lt;br /&gt;&amp;bull;&nbsp;Explore how change happens and revise the campaign plan &lt;br /&gt;&amp;bull;&nbsp;Plan next steps&lt;br /&gt;&amp;bull;&nbsp;Be aware of the other support available&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All Your Skills training sessions are fun and interactive using different methods of learning from team working to self-reflection. You&amp;rsquo;ll also get to work with other volunteers to share your learning. The sessions have been developed to equip you with everything you need in order to be the best in your volunteering role and are led by trained members of staff.&lt;/p&gt;

